                    </a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
        <main>
            <slot />
        </main>
        <footer>
            <h2>External goodies ðŸ¥°</h2>
            <ul class="lenker">
                <li>
                    <a
                        href="https://austingil.com/how-to-build-html-forms-right-semantics"
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noopener noreferrer">Build Html Forms Right</a
                    > By Austin Gil
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a
                        href="https://bhagesh.tech/trick-to-write-css-and-html-100x-faster"
